import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Grid,
  Avatar,
  Typography,
  Button,
  Input,
} from "@material-ui/core";
import "./styles.scss";

export default function MemberShip() {
  return (
    <Box className="container-fluid body-account">
      <Box class="container h-100">
        <Grid container className="h-100" spacing={1}>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <Typography variant="h4">My Account Details</Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3} className="">
            <Box
              className="box"
              sx={{
                padding: "30px",
                borderRadius: "3px",
                backgroundColor: "#333",
              }}
            >
              <Avatar
                className="avatar-member"
                src="https://member.aorus.com/images/pic-default.jpg"
              />
              <Typography
                variant="h5"
                className="text-center my-3"
                color="white"
              >
                Nhocvodanh1908
              </Typography>
              <Box sx={{ textAlign: "center" }}>
                <label className="w-100" htmlFor="contained-button-file">
                  <Input
                    accept="image/*"
                    id="contained-button-file"
                    multiple
                    sx={{ display: "none" }}
                    type="file"
                  />
                  <Button
                    variant="outlined"
                    sx={{
                      color: "#fff",
                      background: "#000",
                      border: "1px solid #fff",
                      width: "100%",
                    }}
                    component="span"
                  >
                    Edit Profile Picture
                  </Button>
                </label>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={9}></Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
